parameters:
Mage Relm: Do you remember what happened before we fought
the dragon?
Mage Relm: It's when we all bumped our fists together...

Thief Nora: I remember! It's the one where we all exchanged
insults together, right?!
Mage Relm: Well, yes... but how about we do that?
Priestess Sophia: Hehe, that sounds nice, doesn't it?
Priestess Sophia: Then, let me start right away--
Clea: Everyone, how about we make it a new charm?

Clea: Until today, we have experienced various things. We
have always been forging ahead... It has been such a
journey.

Clea: So let's do it with something new, as a symbol of our
growth throughout our journey.

Clea: Thank you, Relm-san, for always helping me countless
times. You are not just a lone genius, but you have been
with us.
Mage Relm: Is that so? It's perfect for us!

Mage Relm: Nora-san, I have been saved by your skills and
abilities many times. Thank you for being our friend.

Thief Nora: Sophia-san healed me a lot! She also gave me
bread and showed me her strength and weaknesses without
hiding anything!

Priestess Sophia: Clea-chan, at some point, your
recklessness turned into courage. With that large sword of
yours, you have been cutting through the unknown darkness.

Thief Nora: I also want to say something good about Clea-
san!
Mage Relm: In that case, I also want to say it to everyone!

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, it seems like we all feel the same
way.
Clea: Let's talk about that after everything is over.

Clea: Last time, we fought only for ourselves, but now we
are standing here for a completely different reason.

Clea: For the people we met on our journey, for someone
living in the empire...
Clea: Let's definitely defeat that monster, the dragon.
Clea: He is calling for us.
Clea: Let's go and settle this.
